        "缭衣缝。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "繚"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "part_of_speech": "verb",
      "meaning": "（通“撩”）引申为纷乱、挑动",
      "examples": [
        "缭乱边愁听不尽。",
        "烟眼缭人。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "繚"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "用以固定船帆的绳索",
      "examples": [
