        "缭手"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "繚"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "part_of_speech": "noun",
      "meaning": "祭祀名（祭肺的一种方式）",
      "examples": [
        "八月缭祭。",
        "缭祭。"
      ],
      "traditional_char": "繚"
    }
  ],
  "formations": [
    {
